{"tid":2361184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強致函公安部祝賀首個中國人民警察節 表示與有榮焉 高振邦微博連出8帖表忠","createTime":"2021-01-10T12:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T14:13:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3813bc363dbbfadc32b0f4e0099ddbdf159b2e89","tid":2361184,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e3DK7VgYzBgniJtLTJD6v9d8fFg=/802x641/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A7CJ5GV7UFD27H2FMR4NRJGGOY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe3DK7VgYzBgniJtLTJD6v9d8fFg%3D%2F802x641%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA7CJ5GV7UFD27H2FMR4NRJGGOY.jpeg&h=e185e743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Prd2I3fiiAX-uALfFYcXg7bJyX0=/802x647/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NAFGUOCPRFAZLIEKFTQRS4GWJQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPrd2I3fiiAX-uALfFYcXg7bJyX0%3D%2F802x647%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNAFGUOCPRFAZLIEKFTQRS4GWJQ.jpeg&h=50af454e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1Ib-ZaVXECcH8dj7-jko1Lu7GYo=/802x1093/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WCEHNYXUAVG6JNRR4LMCH7JQLE.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1Ib-ZaVXECcH8dj7-jko1Lu7GYo%3D%2F802x1093%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWCEHNYXUAVG6JNRR4LMCH7JQLE.jpeg&h=c7409670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wBt9gFP2qalZQJoRwGcPR5QwfL8=/802x919/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y7JUCGBTHVEFZDG265QQYCRAOM.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwBt9gFP2qalZQJoRwGcPR5QwfL8%3D%2F802x919%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY7JUCGBTHVEFZDG265QQYCRAOM.jpeg&h=792d6a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V-e0TcI2jSRi0BcVdA72UdR3eZg=/802x971/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/23BYFGF6YJHVXLSDUTCMNPYN44.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV-e0TcI2jSRi0BcVdA72UdR3eZg%3D%2F802x971%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F23BYFGF6YJHVXLSDUTCMNPYN44.jpeg&h=e677e926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x-y7_iUSseEEOmTTb96xUH2ks28=/802x975/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WBM4KLVNPFEVVEU4F5X3AD372Y.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx-y7_iUSseEEOmTTb96xUH2ks28%3D%2F802x975%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWBM4KLVNPFEVVEU4F5X3AD372Y.jpeg&h=30a963c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d5lXKlNu0LGyMHMZSCOxquOatiw=/802x1109/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JVWCUKKONBBKXC4BS266ECWRZU.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fd5lXKlNu0LGyMHMZSCOxquOatiw%3D%2F802x1109%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJVWCUKKONBBKXC4BS266ECWRZU.jpeg&h=786cf989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YIxk2WbNHpnP7gXOBH9t7GVZLCM=/802x804/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNSEA7EQOZBJBHCUFRYI33CNZU.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYIxk2WbNHpnP7gXOBH9t7GVZLCM%3D%2F802x804%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNSEA7EQOZBJBHCUFRYI33CNZU.jpeg&h=ed033894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提起7.21，相信大多數香港人，都會諗起元朗白衣人恐襲期間，香港警察「唔見人」一幕。唔知係攞景定贈慶？中國國務院喺去年7.21事件一周年當日，宣佈由今年起，將每年嘅1月10日定為「中國人民警察節」。<br />\n<br />\n被指喺7.21白衣人恐襲事件唔見人嘅警隊，領軍嘅警務處處長「PK鄧」鄧炳強今日冇玩失蹤，仲透過藍絲最常用嚟圍爐嘅社交媒體「微博」，透露已經第一時間致函公安部，話要代表香港警隊「致以熱烈祝賀」，又話作為警察團隊嘅一分子，「香港警隊與有榮焉」。<br />\n<br />\n但要數「表忠」程度，PK鄧似乎就要向佢下屬、早前由警察公共關係科（PPRB）調任做機動部隊大隊長嘅高振邦學嘢喇，皆因高振邦由噚晚約8點半開始，已經喺佢個微博戶口就呢個「中國人民警察節」瘋狂出po致敬，至今已出咗至少8個，莫非佢調職後真係好得閒，所以特別多時間玩微博？<br />\n<br />\n另外，國家安全部仲趁首個中國人民警察節，推出形象宣傳短片， 畫面中出現咗中環建築群等地標，講到喺祖國最需要嘅地方築牢「無形長城」時，畫面就係電車喺香港行緊嘅縮時攝影，唔知有咩含意？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/W5DYU5QI4JAXJCEHYP4Y6LKUPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FW5DYU5QI4JAXJCEHYP4Y6LKUPI%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7btp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=9330c270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FW5DYU5QI4JAXJCEHYP4Y6LKUPI%2F&h=80491481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/W5DYU5QI4JAXJCEHYP4Y6LKUPI/</a>"},{"pid":"51ef65be49711baf27a1f813def61e926839f43e","tid":2361184,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760f5e7e85220eb4a9ac0b15f30b5e86c9bc1026","tid":2361184,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51ef65be49711baf27a1f813def61e926839f43e","tid":2361184,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10